    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170790/extras/590f324976e813603f6e179aa18338fe.avif?t=1770079503\" width=256 height=64 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170790/extras/d47bb809efba542d04c1ffc869290876.avif?t=1770079503\" width=175 height=159 /></span><br>The objective is to explore each area of the dungeon and collect enough treasure value that reaches the level's goals. Once the goal is reached, Escape to the nearest exit to complete the level.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170790/extras/Capture.PNG?t=1770079503\" /></span><br>The dungeon has strange creatures lurking around and they don't like intruders. Luckily, you're armed with numerous melee weapons to defend yourself from these monsters. The more items you collect, the more aggressive they become.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170790/extras/c55f93a54b40e10b40423561b06beef5.avif?t=1770079503\" width=256 height=64 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 8 Areas to explore<br></li><li> Fight against stealthy and strategic enemies.<br></li><li> Screen Resolution support up to 4K on supported systems.<br></li><li> USB Controller Support (Xbox Recommended)<br></li><li> In-Game upgradables such as weapons, stamina, health, and more.</li></ul>",
